                            🌐 HTML
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" id="exportPDF" class="btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none;">
                            📄 PDF
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" id="exportJSON" class="btn-primary" style="text-decoration: none;">
